      "writtenOn": "2021-06-30T12:33:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Our other user facing configs- jobs.json, tasks.json, supported-branches.json are in JSON, which was the primary reason I had chosen JSON for this (to be consistent). One day if we decide to update everything to proto, it should be easy to update this as well.",
      "parentUuid": "5a2ca8d8_4b2eb542",
